{"id": "1343104409873416275", "channel_id": "1342794357815771196", "type": 0, "author_id": "589115953355423805", "author_name": "magushermes", "author_bot": false, "content": "想說一句大逆風的話啦：\n那些說星辰篇機制跟屎一樣的玩家，是無腦智障一鍵收割免洗手遊玩太多嗎？", "timestamp": "2025-02-23T06:17:24.987000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1342794357815771196", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：V2.1.1 相位对弈联动", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1343104637376397439", "channel_id": "1342794357815771196", "type": 0, "author_id": "589115953355423805", "author_name": "magushermes", "author_bot": false, "content": "我到現在為止打幾場星辰篇下來，除了覺得銀鑰覺醒條件太苛、毒與反擊聯動傷害的換算太苛以外，其他還好吧？", "timestamp": "2025-02-23T06:18:19.228000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1342794357815771196", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：V2.1.1 相位对弈联动", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1343105131209691207", "channel_id": "1342794357815771196", "type": 0, "author_id": "589115953355423805", "author_name": "magushermes", "author_bot": false, "content": "還有改進空間沒錯，但是說整個星辰篇乾脆取消……腦子很好用，請多用用", "timestamp": "2025-02-23T06:20:16.967000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1342794357815771196", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：V2.1.1 相位对弈联动", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1343106448892104807", "channel_id": "1342794357815771196", "type": 0, "author_id": "855461987805822987", "author_name": "shchng.", "author_bot": false, "content": "幸好我不是卡墨這個反擊小丑🤡 \n我不玩反擊\n<@1341930066090917899> 你說是不是啊", "timestamp": "2025-02-23T06:25:31.127000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-02-23T06:32:34.721000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1341930066090917899"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1342794357815771196", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：V2.1.1 相位对弈联动", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1343106668103471125", "channel_id": "1342794357815771196", "type": 0, "author_id": "855461987805822987", "author_name": "shchng.", "author_bot": false, "content": "不過我還是很想噴他們的主線地圖", "timestamp": "2025-02-23T06:26:23.391000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1342794357815771196", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：V2.1.1 相位对弈联动", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1343107162288685066", "channel_id": "1342794357815771196", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "(銀鑰覺醒苛刻的部分特別是銀鑰容易過多或不足，不知是否會有其他銀鑰積鑽上限的方法?\n還有造物連動最好能再加強點，特別是如果之後要往不能回頭商店的話，不同隊伍對於不同面向的造物變成了極需要/極不需要，只是加強黑印以及運氣的重要性\n然後主線現在這樣直接落地打的體驗真的很差\n以及天賦素材獲取量是否該放更多比重在主線，畢竟獲取量的差異可能就會導致體驗上的重大差異，而測試基本上也只能以一個固定的天賦等級來做為參考\n||最後這只是長草期的活動怎一堆人都來吵星辰篇，這些細則還是會改吧||", "timestamp": "2025-02-23T06:28:21.214000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-02-23T06:30:59.419000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1342794357815771196", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：V2.1.1 相位对弈联动", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
